": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1015499, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "We are blind towards good insight and have deviated from the Right Path, and evaded ways of righteousness Thus if You rush and take revenge, it would not be oppression However, You give us more time with Your Continued Kindness and wait to perfect Your Kindness and Grace How many people did You bestow Your Blessings upon and granted an opportunity to repent from the great sin?", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "WA NAMEELO A’NIR RA-SHAADE WA NONAA-FERO TORO-QAS SA-DAADE FA-LAW (FA-IN) A’J-JALTA LAA INTA-QAMTA (LAN TAQAM-TA) WA MAA ZALAM-TA WA LAKIN-NAKA TUMHE-LO A’W-DAN A’LAA YADE-KA (BAD-E-KA) BIL EH-SAANE WA TUN-ZERO TA-A’MMO-DAN LIRRAA-FATE WAL-IMTE-NAANE FAKAM MIMMAN AN-A’M-TA A’LAIY-HE WA MAKKAN-TAHU AN YATOO-BA KUFRAL HOOBE.", "ArabicText1": "وَنَمِيْلُ عَنِ الرَّشَادِ وَنُنَافِرُ طُرُقَ السَّدَادِ فَلَوْ (فَاِنْ) عَجَّلْتَ لَا اِنْتَقَمْتَ (لَانْتَقَمْتَ‌) وَمَا ظَلَمْتَ وَلَكِنَّكَ تُمْهِلُ عَوْدًا عَلٰى يَدِكَ (بَدْئِكَ) بِالْاِحْسَانِ وَتُنْظِرُ تَعَمُّدًا لِلرَّافَةِ وَالْاِمْتِنَانِ فَكَمْ مِمَّنْ اَنْعَمْتَ عَلَيْهِ وَمَكَّنْتَهٗ اَنْ يَتُوْبَ كُفْرَ الْحُوْبِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6