but it was Your clear reasons that saved them How many people did You bestow Your Blessings upon but they rebelled, and gave them more time, but they became stubborn, so You took revenge and destroyed them.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "WA ARSHAD-TAHUT TAREEQA BA’DA AN TA-WAGH-GHALA FIL MAZEE-QE FA-KAANA ZAALLAN LAW LAA HIDAAYATO-KA WA KAANA TAA-E-HAN HATTAA TA-KHALLA-SATHO DALAA-E-LOKA WA KAM MIMMAN WAS-SA’TA LAHU FATA-GHAA WA RAA-KHAIY-TA LAHU FAS-TASH-RAA FA-A-KHAZ-TAHU AKH-ZATAL INTE-QAAME WA JAZAZ-TAHU JO-ZAAZAS SERAA-ME.", "ArabicText1": "وَاَرْشَدْتَهُ الطَّرِيْقَ بَعْدَ اَنْ تَوَغَّلَ فِي الْمَضِيْقِ فَكَانَ ضَالًّا لَوْ لَا هِدَايَتُكَ وَكَانَ طَائِحًا حَتّٰى تَخَلَّصَتْهُ دَلَائِلُكَ وَكَمْ مِمَّنْ وَسَّعْتَ لَهٗ فَطَغٰى وَرَاخَيْتَ لَهٗ فَاسْتَشْرٰى فَاَخَذْتَهٗ اَخْذَةَ الْاِنْتِقَامِ وَجَذَذْتَهٗ جُذَاذَ الصِّرَامِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign1